    add41r3 $p |- ( ( A + B ) + ( C + D ) ) = ( ( A + C ) + ( D + B ) ) $=
      ( caddc co add4 addcom opreq2i eqtr ) ABIJCDIJIJACIJZBDIJZIJODBIJZIJABCDE
      FGHKPQOIBDFHLMN $.
      $([22-Aug-99]$)
  $}

  $( Identity law for addition. $)
  addid2t $p |- ( A e. CC -> ( 0 _10 + A ) = A ) $=
    ( cc wcel cn0 caddc co wceq axaddcom 0cn mpan ax0id eqtrd ) ABCZDAEFZADEFZA
    DBCMNOGDAHIJAKL $.
